  "markdown": "[Skip to main content](https://www.aeluma.com/technology#mainContent) [Skip to footer](https://www.aeluma.com/technology#footer)\n[ ![Aeluma, Inc.](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/files/theme/images/logo-sm.svg) ](https://www.aeluma.com/)\n  * [Home](https://www.aeluma.com/)\n  * [About](https://www.aeluma.com/about)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/about)\n    * [Management Team](https://www.aeluma.com/about/management-team)\n    * [Board of Directors](https://www.aeluma.com/about/board-of-directors)\n    * [Certification & Compliance](https://www.aeluma.com/about/certification-compliance)\n  * [Technology](https://www.aeluma.com/technology)\n  * [News](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media)\n    * [Press Releases](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media/press-releases)\n    * [Blog](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media/blog)\n    * [In The News](https://www.aeluma.com/news-media/in-the-news)\n  * [Investors](https://www.aeluma.com/investors)\n    * [Overview](https://www.aeluma.com/investors)\n    * [Company Info](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/company-information)\n    * [IR Calendar](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/ir-calendar)\n    * [Financial Info](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/financial-information)\n    * [Stock Data](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/stock-data)\n    * [SEC Filings](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/sec-filings)\n    * [Governance](https://www.aeluma.com/investors/corporate-governance)\n  * [Careers](https://www.aeluma.com/careers)\n  * [Contact](https://www.aeluma.com/contact)\n\n\n# Technology\n## Disruptive Semiconductors for Mass Markets\nAeluma has developed disruptive semiconductor technology for mobile, AI, defense & aerospace, robotics, automotive, AR/VR, and quantum. Aeluma's proprietary technology combines high-performance compound semiconductors with scalable manufacturing used for mass market microelectronics to facilitate volume production and large-scale integration.\n## Innovative Technology Made Affordable for Consumers\nThe demand for higher performance semiconductors in consumer markets is increasing. This is being driven by AI, AR/VR, robotics, and the electrification and automation of vehicles. Aeluma's disruptive technology is scalable, cost effective, and doesn't sacrifice performance.\n![](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2462/21203/image.jpg)\n## Operations Built for Scalable Manufacturing\nAeluma is based in Goleta, California, considered one of the most important technology hubs in the world. The company operates state-of-the-art R&D and manufacturing capabilities for semiconductor wafer production, quick-turn chip fabrication, rapid prototyping, test and validation. Aeluma also partners with production-scale fabrication foundries, packaging and integration companies. Aeluma maintains extensive patent protection and trade secrets that relate to its materials, manufacturing, chip technology and applications.\n## Applications Across Industries\nAeluma\u2019s technologies are broadly applicable. High-performance and scalable semiconductors are critical for mobile devices, AI, data center interconnects, AR/VR, industrial automation, machine vision, robotics, defense & aerospace, 3D imaging, telecommunications, 5G/6G wireless, and quantum. The opportunities to leverage this technology are nearly endless.\n  * [ ![Visit us on LinkedIn](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21216/icon/icon-linkedin.svg) ](https://www.linkedin.com/company/aeluma \"Opens in a new window\")\n  * [ ![Visit us on X](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21317/icon/icon-x-twitter.svg) ](https://x.com/Aeluma_Inc \"Opens in a new window\")\n  * [ ![Visit us on Instagram](https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2402/21316/icon/icon-instagram.svg) ](https://www.instagram.com/aeluma.inc/ \"Opens in a new window\")\n\n\n\u00a9[Aeluma, Inc.](https://www.aeluma.com/) All Rights Reserved. \n[Privacy Policy](https://www.aeluma.com/privacy-policy) [Disclaimer](https://www.aeluma.com/disclaimer) [Sitemap](https://www.aeluma.com/sitemap)\n",
