ef=\"/investors/ir-calendar\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"\">IR Calendar</a>\n            </li>\n                        <li class=\"has-children\">\n                <a href=\"/investors/financial-information\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"\">Financial Info</a>\n            </li>\n                        <li class=\"has-children\">\n                <a href=\"/investors/stock-data\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"\">Stock Data</a>\n            </li>\n                        <li class=\"has-children\">\n                <a href=\"/investors/sec-filings\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"\">SEC Filings</a>\n            </li>\n                        <li class=\"has-children\">\n                <a href=\"/investors/corporate-governance\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"\">Governance</a>\n            </li>\n                    </ul>\n            </li>\n        <li class=\"\" data-submenu-id=\"submenu-careers\">\n        <a href=\"/careers\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"0\">Careers</a>\n            </li>\n        <li class=\" last-item\" data-submenu-id=\"submenu-contact\">\n        <a href=\"/contact\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"0\">Contact</a>\n            </li>\n    \n</ul>            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</nav>\n\n                    <h1 class=\"sr-only\">Technology</h1>\n                                <main id=\"mainContent\">\n                        <section class=\"module module-full-width primary-color-bg dark\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-image col-lg-6\" style=\"background: url(https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2462/21201/image.jpg);background-position: 50% 50%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: cover;background-color: #333;\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6 \">\n                <div class=\"module-content\">\n                    <div class=\"text\">\n                                            <h2>Disruptive Semiconductors for Mass Markets</h2>\n                                            <p>Aeluma has developed disruptive semiconductor technology for mobile, AI, defense &amp; aerospace, robotics, automotive, AR/VR, and quantum. Aeluma's proprietary technology combines high-performance compound semiconductors with scalable manufacturing used for mass market microelectronics to facilitate volume production and large-scale integration.</p>                                        </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section><section class=\"module no-dark no-overlay bg-position--right neutral-bg center 10-col-layout\">\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-10\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"module-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-area\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Innovative Technology Made Affordable for Consumers</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The demand for higher performance semiconductors in consumer markets is increasing. This is being driven by AI, AR/VR, robotics, and the electrification and automation of vehicles. Aeluma's disruptive technology is scalable, cost effective, and doesn't sacrifice performance.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\t\t\t\t\n\t</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"module row-default-top-image\">\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center flex-row-reverse\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<figure class=\"module-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_20cacd49d68ad2c653c1e05313a006c3/aeluma/db/2462/21203/image.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"module-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-area\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Operations Built for Scalable Manufacturing</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Aeluma is based in Goleta, California, considered one of the most important technology hubs in the world. The company operates state-of-the-art R&amp;D and manufacturing capabilities for semiconductor wafer production, quick-turn chip fabrication, rapid prototyping, test and validation. Aeluma also partners with production-scale fabrication foundries, packaging and integration companies. Aeluma maintains extensive patent protection and trade secrets that relate to its materials, manufacturing, chip technology and applications.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\t\t\t\t\n\t</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"module neutral-bg center 12-col-layout\">\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"module-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-area\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Applications Across Industries</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Aeluma\u2019s technologies are broadly applicable. High-performance and scalable semiconductors are critical for mobile devices, AI, data center interconnects, AR/VR, industrial automation, machine vision, robotics, defense &amp; aerospace, 3D imaging, telecommunications, 5G/6G wireless, and quantum. The opportunities to leverage this technology are nearly endless.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\t\t\t\t\n\t</div>\n</section>\n        </main>\n        <footer id=\"footer\" class=\"top-border-gradient--reverse \">\n    <div class=\"footer-main\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"row justify-content-between align-items-center\">\n                <div class=\"col-